&lt;h2&gt;Staff Nurse&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you an experienced or Newly Qualifed Nurse ready for a new challenge? Do you thrive on providing acute nursing care to a diverse range of surgical patients? Do complex surgical procedures interest you? If yes, then we would love to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;E3 Ward at Queen Alexandra Hospital is looking to recruit Registered Nurses. Our general surgical ward specialises in Colorectal Surgery - home of robotic surgery. Working alongside a multiple disciplinary team you will be mentored and nurtured by a friendly team of experienced colorectal nurses providing you with everything you need for a happy and successful career at PHU.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;E3 has recently undergone a full refurbishment and offers a brand new working environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer you skills and opportunities in:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Acute Pain Management;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Complex wound therapy;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Total Parental Feeding;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Central Line Devices;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Practice Supervisors/Assessor training;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compassionate Leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a dedicated learning and development team here at PHU with opportunities to participate in bespoke in-house surgical training being taught by our very own specialists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PHU offer lots of staff beneits including the use of our on-site Gym and swimming pool and access to our amazon locker facilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One of our experience Health Care Support Workers who is currently enrolled on the Under-graduate Adult Nursing programme says “E3 is a wonderful place to come and learn. I thrive on a challenging environment and with the support of the nursing team I am excited to be completing my nursing programme. I also look forward to working as an RN on E3 in the near future. I don’t just consider the team on E3 my colleagues. I consider them my family”.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal visits are welcomed.Please contact Annie Munks, Ward Manager on ext. 6611 for any further details or queries.&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: 20/11/2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interview date: 30/11/2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
